	<!-- MCM: untagged-mag auto-load -->
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_load">
		<text>Auto-Load Untagged Mags</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_load_desc">
		<text>When you press the load hotkey on a magazine with no mark, automatically pick compatible ammo from your inventory using the preferences below.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_pref_general">
		<text>Untagged Pick: Other mags</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_pref_general_desc">
		<text>Preferred ammo group for untagged non-shotgun mags. "Most plentiful" loads whatever compatible round you carry the most of. A partially loaded mag always tops up with the group already inside it.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_pref_shotgun">
		<text>Untagged Pick: Shotgun</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_pref_shotgun_desc">
		<text>Preferred ammo group for untagged shotgun mags. "Most plentiful" loads whatever compatible shell you carry the most of. A partially loaded mag always tops up with the group already inside it.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_pref_sniper">
		<text>Untagged Pick: Sniper</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_untagged_pref_sniper_desc">
		<text>Preferred ammo group for untagged sniper mags (long-range calibers: 7.62x54R, .300 WM, .338, .50 BMG, 12.7x55). "Most plentiful" loads whatever compatible round you carry the most of. A partially loaded mag always tops up with the group already inside it.</text>
	</string>
