	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_key_load_mag">
		<text>Load Hovered Magazine</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_key_load_mag_desc">
		<text>While the inventory is open, load the magazine under the cursor with the most plentiful ammo of its marked group. An unmarked magazine auto-picks compatible ammo using the Auto-Load settings above.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_key_unload_mag">
		<text>Unload Hovered Magazine / Weapon</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_key_unload_mag_desc">
		<text>Unload the marked magazine under the cursor, or unload/eject the weapon under the cursor. Works on unmarked magazines too.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_key_loadout_mag">
		<text>Toggle Loadout / Eject Weapon</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_magazines_hotkeys_key_loadout_mag_desc">
		<text>Add or remove the magazine under the cursor from your loadout, or eject/unload the weapon under the cursor.</text>
	</string>

